    "The existing cohesion indices did not enter the top 10 decisive features set.",
    "This indicated that LLMs showed larger effects than the existing indices in degree expressions proficiency classification.",
    "Further, this rank also suggested that larger LLMs such as LLaMA2 and GPTNeo showed efficacy, but they may not necessarily give better performance than the smaller ones in detecting L2 learners' degree expressions proficiency.",
